comments: Sabonis (SAC) brings his hand toward the ball and marginal contact occurs with Jokic (DEN) as he receives the entry pass in the post.
Sabonis (SAC) moves alongside Jokic's (DEN) path and marginal contact occurs at the end of the drive prior to Jokic's pass.
Monk (SAC) brings his hand toward the ball and marginal brush contact occurs as Jokic (DEN) gathers the ball and releases his pass.
Barnes (SAC) firms up over his right leg in Gordon's (DEN) path and does not deliver any illegal contact when setting the pick.
Gordon's (DEN) hand grazes Fox's (SAC) back during the driving floater attempt and the contact is marginal.
Fox (SAC) brings his hand directly to the ball and deflects it away from Jackson (DEN) during his dribble around the perimeter.
Barnes (SAC) jumps into the air and avoids making illegal contact with Holiday (DEN) during his contest of the driving shot attempt.
Monk (SAC) brings his arm across his body and avoids making illegal contact with Holiday (DEN) during his contest of the driving shot attempt.
Sabonis (SAC) positions himself in front of Jokic (DEN) and does not deliver any illegal contact when setting the pick.
Fox (SAC) leans into Jokic's (DEN) space and contact occurs that affects his SQBR during the drive.
Braun (DEN) commits a take foul on Monk (SAC).
Braun (DEN) grasps and immediately releases the back of Fox's (SAC) jersey as the shot travels toward the basket and the contact is marginal.
Jokic (DEN) taps the ball as he gathers the pass from Gordon (DEN) and then legally begins his dribble shortly thereafter.
Sabonis (SAC) does not have his right arm in a legal vertical position when arm contact occurs with Jokic (DEN) during his upward shooting motion, which impacts his jump shot attempt.
Watson (DEN) releases the ball prior to coming down out of bounds.
Sabonis (SAC) closes out to a spot in front of Jokic (DEN) and marginal body contact occurs after Jokic releases the ball and has returned to the floor.
Play is stopped due to a clock malfunction. After communication with the Replay Center, the game clock was corrected to 00:00.8 seconds remaining with Sacramento retaining possession.
